{
  "stem": "7938.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the ghetto was created at the end of '41.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at the beginning of '42, we came in, and we got an apartment at the edge street, on the edge of the ghetto, which was, the name was [?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Rinkafka. ?] And there was a house and we got-- one family lived there, but there were two rooms.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had one room, and they had another room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we started looking around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father did, when he needed to go out of the-- of the ghetto, he could get permission from time to time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't work at that time at all, because I didn't have anything in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no real work in the ghetto, unless you work outside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "However, the-- the women could work already because there was a factory of uniform, which was outside of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But every day in the morning, they assembled in the ghetto and they went out there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They called it Optima, because this was the name of the place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Later on, this whole workshop was moved to the ghetto and it was administered there by-- by the people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister and my wife worked there in Optima.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we got married just before this, before entering in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My wife, it was-- her name was Irene.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was with her mother and with her brother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I knew-- knew them very well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And later on, I worked with-- with her brother, and we worked almost at the same place all the time, wherever I took a job.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "However, before I go further, I want to say that something terrible happened in the very beginning when we came into the ghetto, just after three or-- three months, maybe.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
